<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .api-info {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: left;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .api-info h2 {
            color: #667eea;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .api-info ul {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .api-info li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            color: #555;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .api-info code {
            background: #e0e0e0;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .status {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #4caf50;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>🎓 Campus Event Hub</h1>
        <p>Welcome to the Campus Event Hub Backend!</p>
        
        <div class="status">✓ Server is Running</div>

        <div class="api-info">
            <h2>📚 Available API Endpoints</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><code>POST /api/users/register</code> - Register a new user</li>
                <li><code>POST /api/users/login</code> - Login user</li>
                <li><code>GET /api/users/me</code> - Get current user (Protected)</li>
                <li><code>PUT /api/users/update-profile</code> - Update profile (Protected)</li>
                <li><code>GET /api/events</code> - Get all events</li>
                <li><code>GET /api/events/:id</code> - Get event by ID</li>
                <li><code>POST /api/events</code> - Create event (Protected)</li>
                <li><code>PUT /api/events/:id</code> - Update event (Protected)</li>
                <li><code>DELETE /api/events/:id</code> - Delete event (Protected)</li>
                <li><code>POST /api/events/:id/register</code> - Register for event (Protected)</li>
                <li><code>POST /api/events/:id/unregister</code> - Unregister from event (Protected)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: #999;">
            Built with Node.js, Express, MongoDB, and EJS
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
